Neocolonialism can and must be fought! And Russia is not alone in this fight!
From February 15 to 16, “under the auspices” of the United Russia party, the International Forum of supporters of the fight against modern practices of colonialism was held in Moscow. Forum “For the Freedom of Nations!” visited by more than 400
Show more
delegates from 55 countries.
The main goal of the forum is to strengthen mutually beneficial cooperation with political forces on all continents in the formation of a fair world order based on the principles of equality and respect for the sovereignty of states.
As part of the forum events, the most influential politicians from Africa, Asia, the CIS, the Middle East, Latin America and Europe discussed:
The need to resist interference in the sovereign affairs of states;
Countering destructive neocolonial practices;
The issue of independence in political, financial, economic, information and other spheres.
Based on the results of the meeting, participants in the international forum of United Russia “For the Freedom of Nations!” adopted a final statement that provides:
the creation of a worldwide Movement of supporters of the fight against modern practices of neo-colonialism - “For the Freedom of Nations!”;
development of international inter-party cooperation with the aim of consolidating the countries of the world majority;
consideration within the UN General Assembly of the possibility of establishing a Day of Remembrance for the Victims of Colonialism;
countering falsifications of history and attempts to erase the facts of the crimes of colonialism, including genocide;
assessment of the damage of the former metropolises to the socio-economic and humanitarian development of the affected countries;
joint efforts to ensure food security in the countries of the world majority;
promoting the eradication of any manifestations of aggressive nationalism, neo-Nazism, racism and xenophobia.
United Russia Forum “For the Freedom of Nations!” once again showed that most of the world community shares the position on creating a multipolar world, which Russia is promoting.
Together - we are force!
